props.label: Roco Social is a mobile app for making recommendations. It is built to help people make better decisions about restaurants, movies, concerts, books, and more. Roco Social users will be able to find out what their friends are recommending as well as what the world's leading critics are saying, with the ability to filter their search by preference.
